<title>复工后跟新来的同事聊了下，我想辞职了</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/KolAjK7tE4</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/KolAjK7tE4</guid>
<description>&lt;p data-mpa-powered-by=&quot;yiban.io&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;最近全国大部分企业已经正式复工，大家也都开始了忙碌的职场生活。但在大环境的影响下，公司难免会有缩招、降薪、裁员等行动，弄得人心惶惶。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这段时间，很多人经常有这样的问题：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote data-type=&quot;2&quot; data-url=&quot;&quot; data-author-name=&quot;&quot; data-content-utf8-length=&quot;62&quot; data-source-title=&quot;&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;
&lt;section readability=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;8&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;毕业2年，我每天加班加点工作，老板就是看不到我的付出；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;工作过程觉得很吃力，一坐下就被工作任务赶着走，很心累；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;现在裁员风波越来越严重，感觉自己没什么竞争力，我该怎么办&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;为什么线上面试的我拿不到offer？是不是哪里出了问题？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;如今早已不是努力就能成功的时代了，只知道埋头苦干，日复一日做同样的工作，迟早在职场被踢出局。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;这不是在贩卖焦虑，而是提醒我们，必须用有限的时间做更多、更价值的事情，才能提升自己的核心竞争力。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; 1 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;月末，&lt;span&gt;小成&lt;/span&gt;忙着填写各种表格。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section data-role=&quot;outer&quot; label=&quot;Powered by 135editor.com&quot; helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-role=&quot;outer&quot; label=&quot;Powered by 135editor.com&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-id=&quot;92737&quot; data-tools=&quot;135&amp;#x7F16;&amp;#x8F91;&amp;#x5668;&quot;&gt;&lt;section data-width=&quot;100%&quot; readability=&quot;3.5&quot;&gt;&lt;section readability=&quot;7&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;早上到公司一打开电脑，就被满屏的消息轰炸，“报销单这项怎么填？”“工资的税是怎么扣的？”......一上午的时间小成都在做“客服”的工作。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;领导让他做一份年度汇总表，他又打开好几个窗口，目不转睛盯着屏幕，&lt;strong&gt;一栏一栏复制粘贴、&lt;/strong&gt;数据相加，一个不小心粘贴错行，整个表格都要重新校对...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages __bg_gif&quot; data-cropselx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropselx2=&quot;546&quot; data-cropsely1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropsely2=&quot;409&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6244131455399061&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;639&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/OIibazjwrPXOyEEL59omUy6nibRVOp7aNrkyjQI83qa2o7ibX5KYyI9akvRLjALqWmXn3GJtlDXe3kJWetLSLrGsw/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; right=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;图片源自网络&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;一抬头，发现同事都下班了，实习生也走了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;小成&lt;/span&gt;继续埋头敲键盘，好不容易整理得七七八八，电脑突然死机，花了大半天时间录入的信息一下子全没了……&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;小成&lt;/span&gt;整个人瘫坐在椅子上，呆呆地看着黑屏了的电脑，只好重新开机，扛着疲惫一行行录入数据，直到凌晨才下班回家。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;没想到，第二天&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;开月度总结会，实习生的各项工作指标完成得都比&lt;span&gt;小成&lt;/span&gt;的好，&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;不仅数据全面，对比清晰，还有图表作为直观的展示，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;领导直接在会上提到，让&lt;span&gt;小成&lt;/span&gt;和实习生多多交流。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;“在公司待了3年，现在却不如一个实习生，你说这叫什么事啊？”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; rg